<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.10.7">
<l>veḷḷainīr veḷḷat taṇainta varavaṇaimēl</l>
<l>tuḷḷunīr meḷḷat tuyiṉṟa perumāṉē</l>
<l>vaḷḷalē yuṉṟamark keṉṟum namaṉṟamar</l>
<l>kaḷḷarpōl kaṇṇa purattuṟai yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Great lord who sleeps calmly in the crashing sea</l>
<l>On the serpent bed which lies in an ocean of white water,</l>
<l>Beneficent one, Death’s agents are always thieves, it seems,</l>
<l>To your people, lord who dwells in Kaṇṇapuram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
